{"tid":1741162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭文傑稱早前被內地拘留期間曾被虐待及毆打","createTime":"2019-11-20T08:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T00:21:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"61bd6e257f9c1da058e32bac00844d96729c98d4","tid":1741162,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:15:45.000Z","msg":"較早前被內地行政拘留15日的英國駐港總領事館香港僱員鄭文傑，表示被拘留期間，曾經被虐待及毆打。<br />\n<br />\n現時已離職並身在英國的鄭文傑，今年八月從香港前往深圳公幹，乘高鐵回港時失聯，其後證實被內地行政拘留，指他涉及嫖娼。他接受英國廣播公司訪問時表示，被內地當局指他於香港煽動政治不穩，被扣留時一度被鎖上手銬、蒙眼並毆打，之後被逼簽署認罪同意書。<br />\n<br />\n鄭文傑表示，他當時曾協助總領事館收集於香港發生的示威活動資料並作報告，被拘留時，被問到英國於香港示威活動的角色，包括向示威者提供甚麼支援。他與英國政府都堅持，相關資料只是觀察的結果。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述英國政府消息透露，英國外相藍韜文已經傳召中國駐英國大使，並表示對鄭文傑的遭遇感到憤怒，表明希望中方檢視相關做法，並追究有關行為。中方暫時未有回應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1493468_1_L_20191120160517.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1493468_1_L_20191120160517.jpg&h=05418cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493468-20191120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493468-20191120.htm&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=11f2ca81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493468-20191120.htm&h=3fb9318d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493468-20191120.htm</a>"},{"pid":"82812105a532868daa04c212563643bc16ff2605","tid":1741162,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"好小野啫<br />\n香港係輪姦加殺埋你"},{"pid":"eccf2ac6c410ffa17e4ffc4169c34dda00648df2","tid":1741162,"uid":36158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"82812105a532868daa04c212563643bc16ff2605","tid":1741162,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"好小野啫<br />\n香港係輪姦加殺埋你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"唔好笑啊<br />\n收皮啦<br />\n全撚部都大件事"},{"pid":"e0e204735ce74c364c0216f0e12ce62e6a1264ec","tid":1741162,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5cdbbad68d818586ffd491373bcfe61deb4a0dc5","tid":1741162,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"希望大家專心區選先<br />\n你而家出黎只會被捕 黑警拉你坐78 24號就投唔到票<br />\n到時區議會失守 政府就可以大大聲同外媒講市民企佢嗰邊<br />\n係同路人就一定會停一停抖一抖<br />\n邊個阻止區選進行就係鬼 因為客觀效果就係保皇得益<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">11月24日 血債票償 踢走保皇黨</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/250a150e3b7bce618995be275d28ff4e/5E448B03/t51.2885-15/sh0.08/e35/c180.0.1079.1079a/s640x640/70179621_135577684418097_5168140313520011975_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F250a150e3b7bce618995be275d28ff4e%2F5E448B03%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2Fc180.0.1079.1079a%2Fs640x640%2F70179621_135577684418097_5168140313520011975_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D109&h=5380aa8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0b6febbbef7ab66b6174dd4c8b9df692b2f40ed","tid":1741162,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82812105a532868daa04c212563643bc16ff2605","tid":1741162,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"好小野啫<br />\n香港係輪姦加殺埋你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:22:41.000Z","msg":"所以佢走返英國先講"},{"pid":"22c054fefa4c689865ab9b5d1b0dca0da9aa7ce1","tid":1741162,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0b6febbbef7ab66b6174dd4c8b9df692b2f40ed","tid":1741162,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82812105a532868daa04c212563643bc16ff2605","tid":1741162,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dis